_fireBaseBackend
Type : null
Default value : null
getFirebaseBackend
Default value : () => { return _fireBaseBackend; }

initFirebaseBackend
Default value : (config) => { if (!_fireBaseBackend) { _fireBaseBackend = new FirebaseAuthBackend(config); } return _fireBaseBackend; }
